snippet.title: BBTV BOXING
snippet.description:
BBTV: British Boxing TV - Boxing News Interviews, biographical Interviews, big fight predictions, fight footage.

Real stories about real people.

We produce video interviews with amateur and professional boxers, coaches, managers, promoters and fans in the UK but predominantly in Manchester where we are based. We have also recently started doing our own social life documentaries visiting some interesting and hard hitting topics 

Established in 2009, our aim was to help young up and coming boxers get some publicity, get their name out and sell tickets and also to catch up with some retired fighters. Over the years BBTV's Chris Maylett and Aky Karim have interviewed some of the biggest names in the sport and continue to bring their unique style and coverage subscribers.

Thank you to current subscribers for watching us. 

Contact us: boxingpress@bbtvgroup.com

BBTV GROUP LTD
